{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2618","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2618/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2618/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2618/events","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/2618","id":12629761,"number":2618,"title":"files external: allow dynamic backend registration","user":{"login":"crazyphil","id":3602847,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/80b874896d761156e43fe06b22afbeda?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd58edf4ad546fe2da11954e6519fffc4.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"80b874896d761156e43fe06b22afbeda","url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil","html_url":"https://github.com/crazyphil","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/crazyphil/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","assignee":null,"milestone":null,"comments":14,"created_at":"2013-03-30t13:05:21z","updated_at":"2013-08-02t13:45:07z","closed_at":"2013-05-25t15:33:48z","pull_request":{"html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/2618","diff_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/2618.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/2618.patch"},"body":"as discussed in pull request https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/2180, i've modified the files_external app to dynamically register backends instead of using a hard-coded list. i've also moved dependency checks into the backend code (where they belong imo) instead of the oc_mount_config class.\r\n\r\nexternal backends will have to register in their app.php, for example:\r\n```php\r\nif (oc_app::isenabled('files_external')) {\r\n\toc::$classpath['oc\\files\\storage\\rapidshare'] = 'apps/files_external_rapidshare/lib/rapidshare.php';\r\n\toc_mount_config::registerbackend('oc\\files\\storage\\rapidshare', array(\r\n\t\t'backend' => 'rapidshare',\r\n\t\t'configuration' => array(\r\n\t\t\t'user' => 'username',\r\n\t\t\t'password' => '*password',\r\n\t\t\t'root' => '&root')));\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nuntil issue #1235 is closed, external backends also will have to make sure that the files_external app was already loaded (which is not the case when the administrator first enables the backend app and then the files_external app) by calling\r\n```php\r\noc_app::loadapp('files_external');\r\n```","closed_by":{"login":"mtgap","id":1097106,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/454a73ee5feeb428d0c163a48903332c?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f52d29a66f285a1d61125dd69ac0766b2.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"454a73ee5feeb428d0c163a48903332c","url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap","html_url":"https://github.com/mtgap","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mtgap/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}